videos.headline: Thompkins' fumble ends Toledo's impressive drive
videos.description: Logan Woodside's pass to Art Thompkins results in a fumble, ending Toledo's long drive.

videos.headline: Ohio 58-yard catch-and-run
videos.description: Nathan Rourke completes a pass to Papi White who takes it 58 yards into Toledo territory.

videos.headline: Quellette rushes for 6-yard Ohio TD
videos.description: A.J. Ouellette takes the carry 6 yards off left tackle to give Ohio its first TD vs. Toledo.

videos.headline: Toledo's Anderson makes toe-dragging interception
videos.description: Toledo's Tycen Anderson intercepts Nathan Rourke's pass but appears to be out of bounds. Replay shows that Anderson kept his feet inbounds for the interception.

videos.headline: Seymour jukes his way into Ohio territory
videos.description: Shakif Seymour breaks a tackle then puts the moves on defenders for a 36-yard run into Ohio territory.

videos.headline: Johnson's TD catch ties the game at 7
videos.description: Logan Woodside connects with Diontae Johnson for a 34-yard touchdown grab to tie the game for Toledo.

videos.headline: Ellis's forced fumble puts Ohio in scoring position
videos.description: Ohio's Bradd Ellis forces Diontae Johnson to fumble after a short reception. Javon Hagan scoops up the fumble and takes it to the Toledo 30-yard line.

videos.headline: Rourke's extra effort helps extend Ohio's lead
videos.description: Nathan Rourke runs an 8-yard quarterback keeper and extends toward the goal line for the Ohio touchdown.

videos.headline: Ohio piles on lead with another touchdown grab
videos.description: Nathan Rourke steps up in the pocket to find Brendan Cope in the end zone for a 12-yard touchdown reception.

videos.headline: Brown gets his second TD
videos.description: Dorian Brown takes the goal-line carry and powers his way into the end zone for his second touchdown on the night.
